        <Parent_String>Lepisma (genus) [300310507], Lepismatidae (family) [300310508], Thysanura (order) [300310472], Insecta (class) [300310470], Hexapoda (subphylum) [300310468], Arthropoda (phylum) [300265687], Animalia (kingdom) [300249395], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
